entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You've infiltrated the lab and elimintated the bosses.
entries.journal_entry_description: Infiltrate the Imperial Research Facility, locate the Mercenary Bosses, and eliminate them.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Locate Kell Lapaz in the Research Facility.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Kell Lapaz thinks he's the boss, but you are here to show him the real boss.
entries.task02_start_message: Out of the corner of your eye, you notice Kell Lapaz.
entries.task02_utterance_wave_1: You will not live to regret this mistake.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Locate Udo Barnet in the Research Facility.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Udo Barnet was one of those guys that always won the fight. Time to teach him a lesson.
entries.task04_utterance_wave_1: Who are you? Oh well, I needed a good target dummy.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Report to Grenz Zittoun that the Mercanary Bosses have been eliminated.
